OL,5, BBC Radio 2 lost a million listeners in
OL,6, its first quarter without Ken Bruce,   
OL,7, after he left the station to join      
OL,8, Greatest Hits Radio (GHR).             
OL,10,FIn his first three months, Bruce       
OL,11,Fattracted just below 3 million         
OL,12,Flisteners to his GHR mid-morning show. 
OL,14,FThat is around 1.25 million more than  
OL,15,Fthe show's previous host Mark Goodier. 
OL,17,FHowever, it is a much lower audience   
OL,18,Fthan Bruce attracted on Radio 2, where 
OL,19,Fhis was the most popular radio         
OL,20,Fprogramme in the UK.                   
